name: Kaskade
description: '''Ryan Gary Raddon''' (born February 25, 1971), better known by his stage name '''Kaskade''', is an American DJ, singer, songwriter, music producer and remixer. ''DJ Times'' voted Kaskade as "America's Best DJ" in 2011 and 2013. ''[[DJ Magazine|DJ Mag]]'' named Kaskade fifty-first on its 2009 list of Top 100 DJs.
